('d26e76a1-bd20-431e-973b-4c8a99213c38', 'ddefce13-7528-43be-aec5-5bf347b432bf', '1.10', 'use the relationship between final speed, initial speed, acceleration and distance moved: (final speed)2=(initial speed)2+(2× acceleration × distance moved), v2=u2+(2× a× s)', false),
